  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t如图，今年起多地的人防，防空办公室被撤销改组为“国防动员办公室”，其主任往往由发改委的主任（中共的计划经济哨狗）来兼任，瞬间让习包子在基层民防体系之中手眼通天。<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>结合近期降低军队在战时状态受到刑法的限制</b>，这次的大规模动作，可以看作是习包子谋划利用战时状态超越法律，控制各地的第一步。地方民兵被全面接管，也是为了预防调动民兵喊出“敌在中南海！”的“明智光秀”。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNjhmNTI5ZWI5NmI5MGExZmQ2NzM2LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/68f529eb96b90a1fd6736.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/68f529eb96b90a1fd6736.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/68f529eb96b90a1fd6736.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDUxYWMwYTMzNWQxYTg5YzI3YWMxLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d51ac0a335d1a89c27ac1.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d51ac0a335d1a89c27ac1.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d51ac0a335d1a89c27ac1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODNmMGY1ZWEyNGEwMjBmNTVmZjMyLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/83f0f5ea24a020f55ff32.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/83f0f5ea24a020f55ff32.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/83f0f5ea24a020f55ff32.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTRmOWI4OTM5ZmRmYzk4YTU0MWVhLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a4f9b8939fdfc98a541ea.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a4f9b8939fdfc98a541ea.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a4f9b8939fdfc98a541ea.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOGI3NGFlNWQxYWEwOWMzZmI5MTU4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" ta